snippet.title: Shoppe Keep 2 - Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Releasing in Early Access on 26th April 2018: http://store.steampowered.com/app/684580/Shoppe_Keep_2/

Shoppe Keep returns bigger and better than ever! Build a business empire, battle mobs and monsters. It’s merchandising mayhem as you attempt to sell all sorts of fantastical stock to make your millions.
